data.description: NO HOA! Do you want to be a part of the growing and ever-improving, charming community of Noblesville?  This home is perfect for starting your journey to building wealth with ownership and equity in your own home. No need to rent. This beauty features 3 bedrooms and 2 full updated baths, large great room.  The large Primary bedroom has ensuite and walk in closet.  Through the sliding door from the Primary bedroom step out onto to the large deck, overlooking the very large backyard.  The big kitchen is ideal for 2 cooks at the same time.  Check out the huge fenced backyard, it is a perfect place for the fur babies as well as the two-legged ones too.  This home is close to Grand Junction Park and 30 minutes to Grand Park, and Morse Reservoir.  Close to shopping, restaurants and major thoroughfares and mere minutes to Historic downtown Noblesville. Updates by the previous owner include: Carpet (2020), Engineered Hardwood (2019), new Garage Doors and opener, the HVAC system replaced in 2021. Newer washer and dryer (2021) stays with the home.  The home has been a rental for the last 2 years. May need some paint touch up. Again, NO HOA.
